Installation guide
==================

Configure radius
----------------

Add attribute to dictionary. For example add line
$add attribute 160 GLDN-MRadClient-Unifier val_type=String
to file $RADIUS_ETC/subdicts/dict.gldn

Setup this attribute in $RADIUS_ETC/behaviour.
For example add line:
  REQ:GLDN-MRadClient-Unifier = "" . RAD-Authenticator,

Create/edit interface description in $RADIUS_ETC/configuration.
Like this:
interface (name="RadiusClient",
       sendattr="RAD-Identifier",    # <-- it's important
       sendattr="RAD-Code",
       sendattr="Target-Server",
       sendattr="User-Name",
       sendattr="User-Password",
       sendattr="CHAP-Password",
       sendattr="CHAP-Challenge",
       sendattr="Service-Type",
       sendattr="Calling-Station-Id",
       sendattr="Called-Station-Id",
       sendattr="Connect-Info",
       sendattr="NAS-Port",
       sendattr="NAS-Port-Type",
       sendattr="NAS-Port-Id",
       sendattr="NAS-IP-Address",
       sendattr="NAS-Identifier",
       sendattr="State",
       sendattr="Class",
       sendattr="Acct-Status-Type",
       sendattr="Acct-Session-Id",
       sendattr="Acct-Multi-Session-Id",
       sendattr="Framed-IP-Address",
       sendattr="Acct-Input-Octets",
       sendattr="Acct-Output-Octets",
       sendattr="Acct-Input-Gigawords",
       sendattr="Acct-Output-Gigawords",
       sendattr="Acct-Input-Packets",
       sendattr="Acct-Output-Packets",
       sendattr="Acct-Terminate-Cause",
       sendattr="Timestamp",
       sendattr="Acct-Delay-Time",
       sendattr="Acct-Session-Time",
       sendattr="WISPr-Location-Name",
       sendattr="Radclient-Query-Id", # <-- it's important
       sendattr="Tunnel-Server-Endpoint",
       sendattr="Tunnel-Client-Endpoint",
       sendattr="Tunnel-Type",
       sendattr="Framed-Protocol",
       sendattr="GLDN-MRadClient-Unifier", # <-- it's important
       # -c 10 -- we run 10 radclients
       # -u GLDN-MRadClient-Unifier -- use appropriate retry-indicator
       # -r -- remove retry-indicator, do not transmit it to radclient
       prog="/home/michurin/mradclient -c 10 -u GLDN-MRadClient-Unifier -r -- /usr/local/lib/openradius/radclient -C -c 1 -t 6",
       recvattr="int", # obligatory, module screws response chain otherwise
       recvattr="Radclient-Query-Id", # this is not added automatically
       recvattr="RAD-Code",
       recvattr="State",
       recvattr="Class",
       recvattr="Framed-IP-Address",
       recvattr="Session-Timeout",
       recvattr="Idle-Timeout",
       recvattr="Reply-Message",
       recvattr="Acct-Interim-Interval",
       recvattr="VimpelCom-Security-Level",
       recvattr="VimpelCom-Upstream-Bandwidth",
       recvattr="VimpelCom-Downstream-Bandwidth",
       recvattr="Cisco-AVPair",
       flags=Ascii + Short-Attr,
       window=2048,
       jobticket="Radclient-Query-Id",
       timeout=20)                     # interface guard timeout

